description:
82A ROWE TCE, DARRA

Bring Offers.

This gorgeous soon-to-be completed Darra Metricon home (Metricon has pencilled in final clean 1st February, 2023!) presents as a wonderful opportunity not to be missed. Turf has been laid.

Stepping inside you’ll discover an open-plan and tastefully designed layout that features stunning spotted gum hybrid flooring underfoot and crisp antique white usa walls throughout that make the home feel luxurious, welcoming and bright.

The gourmet kitchen features caesar stone benchtops, stylish white absolute gloss cabinetry and a walk-in pantry with a fridge space. Flowing from here is the open-plan living area that connects outside to the expansive entertainer’s deck (approx 7m x 3.5m) from which you can dine with guests as you enjoy picturesque views over the neighbouring park.

In the master suite you’ll find a walk-in robe and ensuite, bedrooms two, three and four each feature built-in robes, and competing the layout is the main bathroom, the laundry and the double garage.

This wonderful family home is set back from the road and enjoys its own entrance, enhancing the peaceful and private feel it offers. Relax in the back yard with the beautiful kookaburras and stunning Rosellas off your back deck and main bedroom, with views to the park.

The sought-after location places those who live here an easy walk from Darra Train Station, shops, dining options, schools, parks and transport links, and less than 30-minutes from the CBD.

Inspection times are flexible, contact me today to arrange.

The garage door, front concrete and patio decking is currently in progress and for now has been added in photos for illustration and approximate end result vision.
